These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, coffee, lemonade, tea
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: crime, family, satire, western, zombie
There are 5 different nationalities: british, chinese, egyptian, malaysian, turkish
City: hamburg, berlin, edinburgh, prague, rome
 1. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 2. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 3. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 4. the person drinking coffee is the person drinking coffee##1
 5. the person traveling to hamburg is the person watching crime movies##1
 6. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 7. the british is on the left of the egyptian##1
 8. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
 9. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
11. the person drinking tea is between the chinese and the person watching zombie movies##2
12. the malaysian is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
13. the turkish is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Beverage      | 7up        | almond-milk | tea     | coffee   | lemonade |
| Movie-Genre   | satire     | family      | western | zombie   | crime    |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | chinese     | british | egyptian | turkish  |
| City           | berlin | edinburgh      | rome     | prague   | hamburg     |

