.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: snowboarding, volleyball, basketball, cricket, rugby
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: country, d&b, disco, r&b, techno
There are 5 different nationalities: chinese, dutch, indian, polish, spanish
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, quad-bike, roller, scooter, skateboard
 1. the person driving the skateboard is in the middle##1
 2. the fan of techno is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 4. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the dutch##1
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is between the chinese and the fan of techno##2
 6. the person driving the scooter is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 7. the fan of country is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 8. the indian is the fan of r&b##1
 9. the indian is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
10. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
11. the indian is the person who's sport is basketball##1
12. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Sport         | cricket | snowboarding | rugby    | volleyball  | basketball    |
| Music-Genre   | techno    | d&b       | disco      | country | r&b        |
| Nationality   | spanish   | dutch     | chinese    | polish  | indian     |
| Transport     | roller    | quad-bike | skateboard | scooter | helicopter |

