City: prague, hamburg, colone, miami, rome
There are 5 different nationalities: british, egyptian, indonesian, japanese, pakistani
 1. the egyptian is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 3. the person eating onion is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
 4. the pakistani is between the person traveling to miami and the person eating tomato##2
 5. the person eating onion is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 6. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the indonesian##1
 7. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person traveling to hamburg##1
 9. the person traveling to rome is in the middle##1
10. the person traveling to miami is the british##1
11. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
12. the british is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
13. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| Food          | watermelon  | papaya     | tomato   | onion     | artichoke |
